Condé Nast Traveller has named Ballyfin the grandest hotel in Ireland  . 
  The 18th century manor house is at the foot of the Slieve Bloom Mountains . 
  Kim Kardashian and Kanye West stayed at the hotel on their honeymoon last year . 
  The hotel has only 20 rooms and can be hired out for £18,000 a night . 
 